adp
---

- Run root-oriented templates diring fetch for user

alterator-domain-policy
-----------------------

1. Share templates
[root@dc0 ~]# mkdir /var/lib/samba/sysvol/alt.domain/templates
[root@dc0 ~]# mount /usr/libexec/adp /var/lib/samba/sysvol/alt.domain/templates -o bind

2. Mandatory postscript policy (/var/lib/samba/sysvol/alt.domain/templates/Policies/postscript at the end

3. alterator-domain-policy layout: Policies | { User }{ Machine }
					      <all policies with sid, params, and active mark and checkbox>

4. Active/non-active policies
